{"tid":2025850,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【洗底】TikTok任命美國人Kevin Mayer為CEO","createTime":"2020-05-20T14:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T15:11:06.000Z","uid":48040,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ae814725d2ce0de77261365c69cf455215d0576e","tid":2025850,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:09:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/premium/001087763?exclusive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fpremium%2F001087763%3Fexclusive&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=2b393a70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/premium/001087763?exclusive</a><br />\n<br />\nTikTok任命一位迪士尼(Disney)高管為其新任首席執行官是明智的。美國立法者對這款應用程序安全性的擔憂，令TikTok的中國母公司字節跳動(ByteDance)倍感壓力。需要一位令人安心的美國籍高管。聘請迪士尼前流媒體主管凱文&bull;邁耶(Kevin Mayer)表明，重大計劃正在醞釀之中。目前尚不清楚這些計劃是否包括讓TikTok自立門戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://TikTok是在字節跳動模仿並收購了美國應用程序Musical.ly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FTikTok%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%A8%E5%AD%97%E7%AF%80%E8%B7%B3%E5%8B%95%E6%A8%A1%E4%BB%BF%E4%B8%A6%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BC%E4%BA%86%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%87%89%E7%94%A8%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8FMusical.ly&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=529831af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">TikTok是在字節跳動模仿並收購了美國應用程序Musical.ly</a>後創立的。該應用以其時長不超過1分鐘的用戶原創視頻而廣受歡迎，是自Snapchat以來最成功的新社交媒體平台。這款應用初期在青少年中流行，封鎖期的無聊已使這款應用在早期用戶群之外的人群中更火了。據數據公司Sensor Tower的訊息，截至4月底，TikTok和其在中國的同款應用抖音(Douyin)的下載量已超過20億次。<br />\n<br />\n其實奶共係可以無分國籍的！<br />\n<br />\n--------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=6c08e21c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a>"},{"pid":"b440e8d73acf87a13164ec8925fca7970ca65e74","tid":2025850,"uid":219635,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"最後句奶共無分國界。我絕對認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼佬最勢利，睇吓香港中環班鬼佬先啦，離地又紅<br />\n英美澳歐大企業咪又係奶，講到尾，武漢肺炎過後就會繼續奶，而家外國講2句平衡下自己國民嘅情緒而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5b32108e4e122584895fd203f117d91998a551","tid":2025850,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b440e8d73acf87a13164ec8925fca7970ca65e74","tid":2025850,"uid":219635,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"最後句奶共無分國界。我絕對認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼佬最勢利，睇吓香港中環班鬼佬先啦，離地又紅<br />\n英美澳歐大企業咪又係奶，講到尾，武漢肺炎過後就會繼續奶，而家外國講2句平衡下自己國民嘅情緒而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:16:01.000Z","msg":"呢幾年中國成功輸出自己的價值觀及道德觀去全球"},{"pid":"9a506128cba30f66a983fd667f610bc1e832400d","tid":2025850,"uid":87610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"迪士尼咪又係奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f68bb7ec3dfc8d9fbc58e6223583365df03e26","tid":2025850,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b440e8d73acf87a13164ec8925fca7970ca65e74","tid":2025850,"uid":219635,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"最後句奶共無分國界。我絕對認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼佬最勢利，睇吓香港中環班鬼佬先啦，離地又紅<br />\n英美澳歐大企業咪又係奶，講到尾，武漢肺炎過後就會繼續奶，而家外國講2句平衡下自己國民嘅情緒而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"唔係自己冇民主自由就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b143f5a70495720b1149687df8829b80ed26c48","tid":2025850,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"【回到未來．沈旭暉 005】獨裁者的僱傭兵：中國陶輝、北韓陶輝與烏干達陶輝<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tdbMI